refactor: organize patches directory by nginx version.  Restructure the patches directory to group patch files under subdirectories named by their corresponding Nginx version (e.g., patches/nginx/1.27.1/). This improves readability, maintainability, and scalability of the patch management system, making it easier to locate and manage version-specific patches.  - Created subdirectories for each Nginx version. - Moved existing patch files into their respective version directories. - Ensured no changes to patch file contents or functionality.  This change enhances the project's organization without affecting runtime behavior.
